Tennis ace Andy Murray sparked a social media meltdown after he was mistakenly named a father by a glossy magazine.
The Dunblane sport star was confused with fellow tennis player Andy Roddick who announced he and girlfriend Brooklyn Decker are a parents-to-be
People Celeb Watch posted on Twitter: “Andy Murray and Brooklyn Decker expecting their first child.”
 

This drew a wry response from Murray who said: “Not sure my wife and @andyroddick will be best pleased to find these out via Twitter! #error”
The comment was retweeted almost 2,000 times.

